{"word":"G448 - ἀνίλεως - aníleōs - an-ee'-leh-oce - Without mercy","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνίλεως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aníleōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ee'-leh-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without mercy</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இரக்கமில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without mercy, merciless"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G2436 - ἵλεως - híleōs - hil'-eh-oce/2436\">G2436</a>; <i>inexorable:</i> - without mercy.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1653/1653\">G1653</a>, <a href=\"#/G1654/1654\">G1654</a>, <a href=\"#/G1655/1655\">G1655</a>, <a href=\"#/G1656/1656\">G1656</a>, <a href=\"#/G415/415\">G415</a>, <a href=\"#/G448/448\">G448</a>"}]}